./.title: Introduction
./.body:
Okr Apis
    Version: 1.0.0
    introduction for okr apis and additional apis of other service
    
    
    
    
        Schemes:
        http
    
    
        
        Summary
            Tag: okr
            
        
            
                
                
                    Operation
                    Description
                
                
                
                    
                        GET /okrs/me
                        get current user's okr
        
                    
                    
                        GET /okrs/history/me
                        get current user's okr history
        
                    
                    
                        GET /okrs/history
                        get current user's okr history
        
                    
                    
                        GET /okrs/subordinates
                        get all the submitted okrs of current user's subordinates and other users who haven't submitted okr.
        
                    
                    
                        POST /okrs/without-score
                        all the specific okrs of users without score in the user list
        
                    
                    
                        POST /okrs/with-score
                        all the specific okrs of users in the user list
        
                    
                    
                        PUT /okrs
                        create or update a specific okr
        
                    
                    
                        PUT /okrs/evaluate
                        evaluate okrs
        
                    
                    
                        PUT /okrs/publish
                        publish okrs
        
                    
                    
                        PUT /okrs/confirm
                        confirm okrs
        
                    
                    
                        PUT /okrs/{okrId}/evaluation
                        update okr evaluation
        
                    
                    
                        PUT /okrs/{okrId}/grade
                        update okr grade
        
                    
                    
                        PUT /okrs/{okrItemId}/score
                        update leader score of okr item
        
                    
                
            
            Tag: organization
            
        
            
                
                
                    Operation
                    Description
                
                
                
                    
                        GET /organizations/relative/{userId}
                        get user's relationship in organization
